title: Scott Disick shares nude photo of Kourtney Kardsahian on Instagram
text:
Scott Disick still has the hots for Kourtney Kardashian.
On Thursday morning, the troubled reality star posted a photo of Kardashian’s backside from her Brian Bowen Smith nude photo shoot .
“Now that’s 1 hot mama,” he captioned the grainy image zoning in on her plump backside.
Disick , 32, has kept quiet since splitting with the mother of his three kids back in July, but he’s returned to taking nightclub gigs and is indulging in alcohol again .
Kardashian, 36, on the other hand, has been more contemplative since the breakup. She’s taken a few trips with friends and posted a number of reflective posts.
Viewers can catch Kardashian’s initial reaction to seeing photos of Disick canoodling with another woman on Sunday’s episode of Keeping Up with the Kardashians .
 The photo Disick shared has 118,000 likes so far. This article originally appeared on the New York Post .
Originally published as Scott Disick is still drooling over Kourtney
